{"tid":2341651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"簡淑兒逼爆小T恤　網民：好胸險！","createTime":"2020-12-26T14:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T14:42:14.000Z","uid":168978,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b73c7523cf7eae25e23e4ea2e598ec8600c8cc7f","tid":2341651,"uid":168978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"曾經做過東網《區區有女神》嘅簡淑兒（Jessica）有份拍攝無綫劇《迷》，在劇中飾演田蕊妮的親女及曾航生的繼女，尋日播出的一集簡淑兒用親生爸爸留畀佢嘅錢去留學，但繼父曾航生就作出干預，簡淑兒因而與繼父曾航生不和。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡淑兒亦都Cap低呢幕放上社交網，希望宣傳下套劇，點知網民就放錯重點，話說Jessica嘅戲服係緊身T-shirt，令到佢上圍呈現逼爆效果，網民留言謂：「上身身材好似有轉變變大咗？」、「好胸險！」、「身材好左咁」、「睇唔出咁好身材」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從簡淑兒演出《愛．回家之八時入席》後人氣急升，成為一眾網民新寵，更被封係仙氣女神，仲話佢似初出道嘅Angelababy，唔怪得知求其POST張相，網民都咁大反應啦！"},{"pid":"b5551b0ac4662c3bb72bdfdf5508e6cbb4b4526e","tid":2341651,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"我入到來.."},{"pid":"4a4727868054822a5cc324149a8034847c7ee686","tid":2341651,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">簡淑兒我愛你<br />\n#168978</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">起底＞專開無圖垃圾post</span>"},{"pid":"24cd32170e882b0fe3cd861d8431f9984d36fc9c","tid":2341651,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a4727868054822a5cc324149a8034847c7ee686","tid":2341651,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">簡淑兒我愛你<br />\n#168978</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">起底＞專開無圖垃圾post</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 block左佢先"},{"pid":"86ab903d728a0851a8ef8d10f2ce293b821cd4ee","tid":2341651,"uid":169492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"10秒都唔會俾你"},{"pid":"9ab7352a3e71fe344fda606d8c85f2cacbcc15ef","tid":2341651,"uid":53959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cite